ENAMvel is copied from GASC. (don't have good ref yet for ENAM model)
RIFSISvel is copied from SIMA
ORZ0 is a very crude model. Below 10 km it is the average crust from Christensen & Mooney 1995. 
                            Above 4 km depth, the abstract Moffat et al. 2021 (AGU meeting) says Vp < 5.5 km/s.

oiink.taup is copied from gasc.taup
